## Glossary

- **DNOTAM**: Digital Notice to Airmen
- **Service Definition**: SWIM Registry document defining service interfaces and behavior
- **Yellow Profile**: EUROCONTROL SPEC-170 - protocol and infrastructure requirements for ALL SWIM services
- **ED-254**: EUROCAE Standard for Extended AMAN only (NOT applicable to DNOTAM)
- **CP1**: Common Project 1 (SESAR Deployment)
- **AISP**: Aeronautical Information Service Provider
- **ANSP**: Air Navigation Service Provider
- **AIFS**: Aeronautical Information Flight Service
- **AMAP**: Aerodrome Mapping
- **ePIB**: Electronic Pre-flight Information Bulletin
- **EACP**: European Aviation Common PKI
- **ASM**: Airspace Management
- **LARA**: Local AIS Regional Automation (system)
